---
title: Chesapeake Steak & Lobster Tail with Oven Fries, Creamy Lemon Garlic Sauce & a Mixed Greens Caesar
description: Bring the white tablecloth vibes to your dinner table with this surf ’n’ turf dish. Lobster tails are basted with a rich, smoky Old Bay butter, which is also used to top perfectly seared steaks. The duo’s paired with a crisp mixed greens Caesar salad and oven fries seasoned with more Old Bay, plus a creamy garlic lemon sauce on the side for dipping. Don’t be surprised if you mistake your dinner table for the fancy corner booth at that steakhouse downtown.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chesapeake-steak-lobster-tail-46b30239.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chesapeake-steak-lobster-tail-5f736f155a4171574b7e20c4-1eeda329.pdf
